IMPORTANT NOTICE REGARDING BIBLE CONTENT:

This software is a web scraping tool that downloads Bible translations from
BibleGateway.com. The Bible translations themselves are NOT covered by this
MIT License and remain subject to their respective copyright holders and
license terms.

Each Bible translation has its own copyright and usage restrictions:
- King James Version (KJV) - Public Domain
- New International Version (NIV) - © Biblica, Inc.
- English Standard Version (ESV) - © Crossway
- New Living Translation (NLT) - © Tyndale House Publishers
- And many others...

When using this software:
1. Respect BibleGateway.com's Terms of Service
2. Verify copyright terms for each Bible translation you download
3. Provide proper attribution for the Bible translations in your applications
4. For commercial use, obtain appropriate licenses from copyright holders

This software is intended for personal, educational, and research purposes.
For public or commercial distribution of Bible content, you must comply with
the copyright terms of each specific translation.

The authors of this software are not responsible for any misuse of Bible
content or violations of copyright terms.
